                            <comment id="89759" author="adilger" created="Tue, 22 Jul 2014 17:30:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The test was added in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3469&quot; title=&quot;OSP dt_sync() operation should flush pending destroys and other updates&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3469&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3469&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/10046&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/10046&lt;/a&gt;, which was not landed to b2_5, so this test should be skipped when running against MDS versions older than 2.5.60.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
